to 60% just by following this one rule. 

27
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:48,800
The market is telling you its bias with 
the Zero Line. When MACD is above zero,  

28
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:56,000
buyers are in control. When it's below zero, 
sellers run the show. So stop fighting what  

29
00:02:56,000 --> 00:03:01,520
