This alone will transform your trading.

32
00:03:17,653 --> 00:03:19,280
Part B: The Crossover Entry
Now that the Zero Line gives  

33
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:26,240
us direction, crossovers give us exact timing.
But first, here's the mistake everyone makes.  

34
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:33,200
You take every crossover. You see the lines 
cross and jump in immediately. But 80% of  

35
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:39,280
crossovers happen in what I call the "chop 
zone"—that area right around zero where the  

36
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:44,640
market can't decide what it wants to do.
What's really happening in that zone is  

37
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:51,600
the market is ranging, not trending. MACD is 
flipping back and forth with zero conviction.  

38
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:58,000
You're buying and selling noise. You're trading 
chop. You're donating money to the market. 

39
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:04,400
The solution is stupidly simple—the Distance 
Rule. Only take crossovers that happen far  

40
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:14,080
from the zero line. Above 0.5 or below minus 
0.5 on most charts. That distance proves the  

41
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:19,440
trend has actual power behind it.
Here's the exact technique I use.  

42
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:24,880
When MACD is above zero and you get 
a bullish crossover above this line,  

43
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:32,880
that's a continuation entry. The trend is strong 
and getting stronger. When it's below zero and  

44
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:42,320
you get a bearish crossover below minus 0.5 line, 
that's your short. The downtrend is accelerating. 

45
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:49,680
Look at this chart with me. See this crossover 
near zero? It’s a bad signal. And this crossover  

46
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:56,640
just above the line. Another fake signal.
But check this crossover…that’s a valid  

47
00:04:56,640 --> 00:05:02,240
50-pip move. The distance from 
zero is literally everything. 

48
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:09,440
And here's what separates beginners from people 
who actually make money—wait 2 or 3 candles after  

49
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:16,320
the crossover before entering. Just wait. 
This one rule eliminated maybe half of my  

50
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:23,520
false signals. The market needs time to prove 
the crossover is real, not just a fake move. 

51
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:28,960
This Trend System prints money in trending 
markets, but the Reversal System I'm about to  

52
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:35,760
