Are all three timeframes aligned?  

122
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:17,280
Is price at a key level? Is the histogram 
confirming? If anything is missing, I pass. 

123
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:23,200
Entry happens at candle close, never 
mid-candle. Stop goes at the recent  

124
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:30,640
